==English==
===Acronym===
#Acronym for Mother I'd Like to Fuck. Popularized by the film ''[[w:American Pie_(movie)|American Pie]]'' (1999).
#''(acronym)'' {{vulgar}}: A (putative) [[mother]] found sexually attractive.
#:''Tom's mother is hot &mdash; she's a real '''MILF'''.''
====Pronunciation====
*[[Wiktionary:Pronunciation_key|IPA]]: /mɪɫf/
*[[Wiktionary:Pronunciation_key|SAMPA]]: /mI5f/

====Usage note====
''MILF'' has quickly become a much used descriptor on the internet for pornography sites featuring women mostly between the ages of 35 and 50.

===Initialism===
'''MILF''' 
#Abbreviation of [[w:Moro Islamic Liberation Front|Moro Islamic Liberation Front]], an organization in the Philippines seeking to establish an Islamic state on the island of Mindanao. 

